data.description: Enjoy this 12 Acre approx. 4 Bedroom 2 Full bath Custom ranch home Located in Yale Schools.  Exterior features 3 oak, 27 apple, 10 crab apple, 6 pear, 15 permission, 7 peach, 3 plum, 2 cherry, and 16 chestnut trees , a 60 x 70 pole barn , cement floor, water  and electric.  Barn is partially spray foam insulated.  This property is a nature lovers paradise.  In 2017 home got updates including a new roof , windows, drywall , electric, new kitchen, and a 630 sq foot addition.   This is a must see.
